user_instruction: 'Send an email to Vitality Partners to update them on our HealthHub requirements. You can check out my Gmail and Notion for information.'

formatted_items.content:
Subject: Need the Latest HealthHub Requirements for Vendor Update

Hi Jane,

Could you please pull together the most current list of HealthHub requirements so we can update Vitality Partners?

• Check Gmail: any recent threads with subject lines like “HealthHub Specs,” “Feature Priorities,” or “Employee Feedback.”  
• Check Notion: the “HealthHub Requirements” and “Employee Feedback – Wellness Program” pages for the newest edits or comments.

Once you’ve consolidated everything, could you share the document (or a quick summary) with me by tomorrow afternoon? I’d like to include the latest details in our email to Vitality Partners.

Thank you!

Best,  
[Your Name]
